title: Newly updated one bed in Albany Park; In-Unit Laundry; Pets OK!
posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 259408444', 'Rent: $1,250 / Month', 'Beds: 1', 'Bath: 1', 'Available Date: 07/01/2022', 'Pet: Cats & Small Dogs Only', 'Rent Includes:: Water', 'Parking:: no parking', '4407 North Kimball Ave., #2', 'BRAND NEW FULLY UPDATED UNIT AVAILABLE FOR RENT!', 'Unit includes brand-new stainless-steel kitchen appliances, in-unit washer / dryer and central heating and air!', 'Located in a great location across from local restaurants and convenience stores!', 'Please Call', 'Adam Antonucci', '847-533-0962', 'Residential Sales & Leasing', 'Albany Park is the name of both a community area and a neighborhood on the historic Northwest Side of Chicago.', 'Other neighborhoods in the Albany Park community area include North Mayfair, Kimball, East Albany Park, and Ravenswood Manor.', 'Albany Park has myriad entertainment options, from a branch of the local library to performing arts theater to the Horner Park Farmers Market.', 'The neighborhoods culinary scene is the quintessential melting pot, with a dynamic array of restaurants representing Mexican, South American, Filipino, Korean, Indian, Cambodian, Somali, Romanian, and Middle Eastern cultures.', "This variety means all good things when it comes to grabbing a bite to eat, especially if you're craving Persian rice, refreshing Mexican paletas, or Kyrgyzstani hand-pulled noodles.", 'Taking the 81 bus east on Lawrence Avenue will get you to the Red Line (Lawrence stop) and taking it west will get you to the Blue Line (Jefferson Park).', "There's a bike pathway up and down the North Branch of the Chicago River and there are also buses running north and south along Kimball and Pulaski Avenues and east and west along Montrose and Foster Avenues", '4405 North Kimball Avenue has a Walk Score of 93 out of 100.', 'This location is a Walkers Paradise so daily errands do not require a car.', '4405 N. Kimball Avenue is a nine minute walk from the Brown Line at the Kedzie-Brown stop.', 'FEATURES', 'Cats Ok', 'Ceiling Fans', 'Dishwasher', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Laundry in Unit', 'Microwave', 'Modern Bathroom', 'Modern Kitchen', 'No Smoking', 'Quartz Countertops', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Please Call', 'Adam Antonucci', '847-533-0962', 'Residential Sales & Leasing', 'The Apartment Source', 'Call or text:', '773.404.9900']
